  <h2>Basic 10 Steps to Create a Website from Scratch</h2>
  <p>Creating your own website may seem like a daunting task, but with the right approach and understanding of the basic steps, you can do it easily and effectively. Here are 10 basic steps to get you started:</p>
  <ol>
    <!-- Здесь будут перечислены шаги -->
    <li>Choose a platform for creating your website. Consider various options such as WordPress, Wix, Squarespace, etc., and choose the one that best suits your needs.</li>
    <li>Register a domain name. This will be the address of your website on the Internet, so choose it wisely and make sure it aligns with your brand.</li>
    <li>Select hosting for your website. Hosting is where your website files will be stored and where it will be accessible to visitors.</li>
    <li>Install and configure a CMS (content management system), if you have chosen that path. This will allow you to easily add, edit, and manage your website content.</li>
    <li>Create the design of your website. Choose a template or develop a unique design that reflects your brand and attracts visitors' attention.</li>
    <li>Create the main pages of your website, such as the homepage, about us, services, contact, etc. Ensure they are informative and user-friendly.</li>
    <li>Add content to your website. This can be text, images, videos, graphics, and other materials that will help attract visitors' attention and convey the necessary information.</li>
    <li>Set up SEO (search engine optimization) for your website. This will help your website be better visible in search results and attract more potential customers.</li>
    <li>Test your website's functionality before launching it. Make sure all pages and functionality work correctly, and fix any errors or glitches.</li>
    <li>Launch your website and promote it. Tell your friends and acquaintances about it, use social media and other channels to attract an audience, and gradually develop your online project.</li></ol>
  <p>By following these simple steps, you can create a quality and professional website that will successfully represent your company or project on the Internet.</p>
